A decent game, but it massively drains battery power and freezes in places on the higher levels. The game breaks at level 59. Upon completing the level you rank up to level 60, but instead of loading the new level it freezes on the completion screen for level 59. If you close and reopen the app your most recent progress is lost and you have to finish level 59 once more. You cannot return to previous levels at any point; not great for kids or multiple children playing on one device.
